verbose_text: Upregulation of PD-1L expression on tumor cells increases the effect of pembrolizumab.14 Combination of talimogene laherparepvec and ipilimumab has been evaluated in a phase Ib and phase II studies, both showing higher efficacy in combination than as a monotherapy of talimogene laherparepvec or ipilimumab alone.15, 16 Talimogene laherparepvec intralesional injections before pembrolizumab administration promoted the CD8 + cell infiltration into tumor.
